gov.ornl.keva.table

Class UnsafeBucket

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.ornl.keva.table.TableValue
      • gov.ornl.keva.table.TableBucket
        • gov.ornl.keva.table.UnsafeBucket

  • public class UnsafeBucket
extends TableBucket
    A non-thread-safe bucket implementation used by the sstable readers. When reading from an sstable we know that there is only a single writer.
    Author:
    James Horey
